quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  21,45,"Qul innama onthirukum bilwahyiwala yasmaAAu assummu adduAAaaitha ma yuntharoon"
  21,46,"Wala-in massat-hum nafhatun min AAathabirabbika layaqoolunna ya waylana inna kunnathalimeen"
  21,47,"WanadaAAu almawazeena alqistaliyawmi alqiyamati fala tuthlamunafsun shay-an wa-in kana mithqala habbatinmin khardalin atayna biha wakafa binahasibeen"
  21,48,"Walaqad atayna moosawaharoona alfurqana wadiyaan wathikranlilmuttaqeen"
  21,49,"Allatheena yakhshawna rabbahum bilghaybiwahum mina assaAAati mushfiqoon"
  21,50,"Wahatha thikrun mubarakunanzalnahu afaantum lahu munkiroon"
  21,51,"Walaqad atayna ibraheemarushdahu min qablu wakunna bihi AAalimeen"
  21,52,"Ith qala li-abeehi waqawmihi mahathihi attamatheelu allatee antum lahaAAakifoon"
  21,53,"Qaloo wajadna abaanalaha AAabideen"
  21,54,"Qala laqad kuntum antum waabaokumfee dalalin mubeen"
  21,55,"Qaloo aji/tana bilhaqqiam anta mina allaAAibeen"
  21,56,"Qala bal rabbukum rabbu assamawatiwal-ardi allathee fatarahunna waanaAAala thalikum mina ashshahideen"
  21,57,"Watallahi laakeedanna asnamakumbaAAda an tuwalloo mudbireen"
